npm init -y
npm install bootstrap
npm i bootstrap
npm i bootstrap --save : install command for prior version 5 of nodejs
npm i jquery
npm install bootstrap@5.1.2
npm install bootstrap@4.2
npm install bootstrap@4
npm install boostrap jquery lodash
npm uninstall jquery
npm uninstall bootstrap

npm i : install all packages in package.json file


semantic version:
        2.4.5
  Major.Minor.Patch
Major: incompatible API changes
Minor: add backwards-compatible functionality
Patch: make backwards-compatible bug fix


npm i jquery --save-dev : install as development dependency

npm i command install packages as local module, to install it globally use -g option:
npm i bootstrap@5.3 -g: install it as global package, located in user/appdata/roaming/npm/node_modules

npm list -a: to list installed packages and its dependencies
npm list : to list installed packages
npm list --depth 1 : to list installed packages and dependencies with depth of 1

